<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 57 - 59. Genitalia (proximal parts excluded) (57), internal structure of distal genitalia (58) and transverse section of apical penial papilla (59) of Monacha pantanellii from Lago del Turano [Tur 2] (FGC 41654)." , "Figures 49 - 52. Genitalia (proximal parts excluded) (49), internal structure of distal genitalia (50), transverse sections of medial epiphallus (51) and apical penial papilla (52) of Monacha pantanellii from Valle dell'Aniene, Roccagiovine [Ani] (FGC 42974)." , "Figures 37 - 40. Genitalia (proximal parts excluded) (37), internal structure of distal genitalia (38), transverse sections of medial epiphallus (39) and apical penial papilla (40) of Monacha pantanellii from Monte Fionchi summit [Fio 1] (FGC 8140)." , "Figures 23 - 31. Shell variability in Monacha pantanellii from Via Salaria, Poggio San Lorenzo [Lor] (FGC 41551) (23 - 25), Valle dell'Aniene, Roccagiovine [Ani] (FGC 42974) (26 - 29) and Carsoli [Car] (FGC 41651 (30, 31)." , "Figures 53 - 56. Genitalia (proximal parts excluded) (53), internal structure of distal genitalia (54), transverse sections of medial epiphallus (55) and apical penial papilla (56) of Monacha pantanellii from Carsoli [Car] (FGC 41651)." , "Figures 15 - 22. Shell variability in Monacha pantanellii from Lago del Turano [Tur 2] (FGC 41654) (15 - 17), Via Salaria, Ornaro Alto [Alt] (FGC 41553) (18 - 20) and Vallonina [Val] (FGC 25345) (21, 22)." , "Figures 45 - 48. Genitalia (proximal parts excluded) (45), internal structure of distal genitalia (46), transverse sections of medial epiphallus (47) and apical penial papilla (48) of Monacha pantanellii from Vallonina [Val] (FGC 25345)." , "Figures 5 - 14. Shell variability in Monacha pantanellii from Monte Fionchi, summit [Fio 1] (FGC 8140) (5, 6), Monte Fionchi, Torrecola [Fio 2] (FGC 38944) (7), road to Montenero Sabino [Sab] (FGC 41552) (8 - 10) and Turania [Tur 1] (FGC 42971) (11 - 14)." , "Figures 60 - 63. Internal structure of distal genitalia of Monacha pantanellii from Valle dell'Aniene, Roccagiovine [Ani] (FGC 42974) (60), Via Salaria, Ornaro Alto [Alt] (FGC 41553) (61), Turania [Tur 1] (FGC 42971) (62) and road to Montenero Sabino [Sab] (FGC 41552) (63)." , "Figures 41 - 44. Genitalia (proximal parts excluded) (41), internal structure of distal genitalia (42), transverse sections of medial epiphallus (43) and apical penial papilla (44) of Monacha pantanellii from Monte Fionchi, Torrecola [Fio 2] (FGC 38944)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472725" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472730" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472726" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472720" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472729" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472719" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472731" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472727" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472721" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472728" .

